FIG. 17. –– 

Parapontophilus geminus

n. sp.
, ♀ 11.2 mm,holotype,Hyuga-nada Sea,Japan (RV 
Tansei-maru
, KT05-30,stn HB) (CBM-ZC 8764): 
A
, carapace and cephalic appendages,dorsal view; 
B
, rostrum,dorsal view; 
C
